  "title": "Step 2: Define the stream processor.",
  "description": "An Atlas Stream Processing stream processor applies the logic of a uniquely named\nAggregation pipeline stages to your\nstreaming data. Atlas Stream Processing saves each stream processor definition to\npersistent storage so that it can be reused. You can only use a given\nstream processor in the Manage Stream Processing Workspaces in which its definition is\nstored.",
